Kenya and the continent have lost a true statesman â€” a man who never gave up on the dream of unity and dignity for his people.

So Kenyan people Donâ€™t feel too sad,  Life is like this â€” people come, and people go.
What matters most is the legacy they leave behind.
Raila Odingaâ€™s name, his courage, and his vision will never die.
